Title: House's Head (1)
Plot: A bus accident leaves House with serious head trauma and partial amnesia. He comes to believe that a patient on the bus had a life-threatening disease and struggles to recall who it was, and what they had.
Writer: Russel Friend, Garrett Lerner, Doris Egan, David Fos
GuestStars: Fred Durst, Sharmila Devar, Isaac Bright, Jennifer Lee Wiggins, Rebecca Rhae Larsen, Boogie, Henry Hayashi, Julie Ariola, Ivana Milicevic
